16
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:36,040
=Love and Sword=

17
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:40,480
(Adapted from Shen Cangmei's novel
Sleeping Beside Yan Shao)

18
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:44,010
=Episode 8=

19
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:46,560
I don't doubt you.

20
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,480
I never have.

21
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,670
Thank you, Young Lady Rong.

22
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,640
Can you give me

23
00:02:00,137 --> 00:02:01,515
the flower ball?

24
00:02:15,230 --> 00:02:16,160
What is he...

25
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:20,880
No!

26
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,710
That's beautiful.

27
00:02:26,715 --> 00:02:27,848
(Secrets of Fate Revealed)

28
00:02:57,110 --> 00:02:57,760
Who's there?

29
00:03:15,137 --> 00:03:16,880
Someone is causing trouble
at the flower fair.

30
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:17,782
Go and check it out.

31
00:03:18,472 --> 00:03:20,360
(Blossom's Smile)

32
00:03:47,213 --> 00:03:49,200
It's the Tang Clan's hidden weapon.

33
00:03:54,950 --> 00:03:57,920
What did you add to the wine jar?

34
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,360
When did you find out

35
00:04:01,990 --> 00:04:03,670
that I'm from the Ghost Valley Sect?

36
00:04:09,619 --> 00:04:11,550
Jade Leaf Golden Blossom Wine?

37
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:12,440
You

38
00:04:12,709 --> 00:04:14,760
drank the poisoned wine you brew...

39
00:04:15,459 --> 00:04:17,240
It is fine

40
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,640
for me to repay with my life

41
00:04:18,710 --> 00:04:21,200
to those who perished

42
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:23,680
at your hands.

43
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:30,350
That jar doesn't contain wine.

44
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:32,880
It's poison.

45
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,590
The Celestial Maiden's Blossom.

46
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:39,950
Thank you for granting my request.

47
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,240
So this was all part of your plan.

48
00:05:15,350 --> 00:05:16,320
On Zhonghe Festival,

49
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:19,160
it's a sign of good fortune
when the sky lanterns light up the land.

50
00:05:19,204 --> 00:05:21,350
Consider this my gift to Yuchi Manor.

51
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:22,760
Who are you?

52
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:25,120
A friend, not foe.

53
00:05:26,590 --> 00:05:28,440
That's all you need to know.

54
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,800
How is someone like you

55
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:31,950
willing to serve as a mere guard?

56
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,680
Everyone has their own path.

57
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,830
Tonight, Yuchi Manor was careless.

58
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,120
With Young Lady Rong here,

59
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,150
not necessarily.

60
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,640
She sees everything,
quick-witted and sharp.

61
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,680
Even without her martial skills,

62
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:48,910
her skills in strategies
are truly impressive.

63
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:52,080
Since we're all safe now,

64
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:55,390
shall we take this wine downstairs

65
00:05:55,910 --> 00:05:56,950
and drink it while we chat?

66
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:58,950
Sounds great.

67
00:06:50,093 --> 00:06:51,640
Yuchi Manor isn't being very honest.

68
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,680
This festival is a trap!

69
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:54,315
It's an ambush by Ghost Valley Sect!

70
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,320
Everyone, be careful!

71
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,150
Brother!

72
00:07:27,590 --> 00:07:28,150
The wine!

73
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,880
They are targeting the wine.

74
00:07:30,137 --> 00:07:31,000
It's not wine inside.

75
00:07:31,004 --> 00:07:31,893
It's likely poisoned.

76
00:07:32,026 --> 00:07:33,120
I'll take it away from here.

77
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:34,440
Tell everyone to evacuate.

78
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,120
All right.

79
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:40,150
The wind direction!
Go against the wind direction!

80
00:07:45,182 --> 00:07:46,604
Evacuate the people immediately!

81
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,226
All right.

82
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,359
(East Market)

83
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,337
- Go!
- Get out of here!

84
00:07:57,337 --> 00:07:58,248
Hurry! Get out of here!

85
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,590
Stay safe!

86
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:00,200
Hurry!

87
00:08:52,333 --> 00:08:53,130
(East Market)

88
00:08:56,582 --> 00:08:57,560
(East Market)
Yan Shao!

89
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,040
Rong Shukuang.

90
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,630
If I die from poisoned,

91
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,440
will you cry for me?

92
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,520
Stop spouting nonsense.

93
00:09:04,950 --> 00:09:05,750
You won't die.

94
00:09:06,470 --> 00:09:07,440
I won't allow you to die!

95
00:09:09,470 --> 00:09:10,200
Sister Rong.

96
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:14,350
The wine jar contains

97
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,200
Celestial Maiden's Blossom!

98
00:09:16,950 --> 00:09:17,590
All right.

99
00:09:17,848 --> 00:09:20,400
Celestial Maiden's Blossom
can be neutralized with water.

100
00:09:20,515 --> 00:09:21,470
Evacuate the people.

101
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,560
Move upwind.

102
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,400
Yan Shao,

103
00:09:32,230 --> 00:09:33,440
you have to come back alive!

104
00:09:49,470 --> 00:09:50,080
Help!

105
00:09:57,648 --> 00:09:58,630
Are you all right?

106
00:11:42,543 --> 00:11:44,610
(Red Banner Flower Fair)

107
00:11:45,693 --> 00:11:46,710
Is everyone all right?

108
00:11:46,950 --> 00:11:47,470
Someone.

109
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:55,750
Master Lin,

110
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:58,230
how do you explain
what happened tonight?

111
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:01,110
Rest assured, I'll handle the aftermath

112
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,200
and get to the bottom of this.

113
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,080
Father,

114
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,590
the city is still in chaos.

115
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:07,200
I ask that you and the elders

116
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,710
help protect and evacuate the people.

117
00:12:08,715 --> 00:12:09,909
I'll take a team to track down

118
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,737
the remaining
Ghost Valley Sect infiltrators.

119
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:12,950
Since that's your plan,

120
00:12:12,950 --> 00:12:14,990
the Junshan Sect will lend you a hand.

121
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,710
Thank you, everyone.

122
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:18,630
Chief Jiang,

123
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,830
your son was seen
with the Ghost Valley Sect.

124
00:12:20,830 --> 00:12:22,590
If he really has sided with them,

125
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:24,920
the Seven-Star Hall won't stand by
and do nothing.

126
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,280
Shaoci,

127
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:28,040
I leave this place to you.

128
00:12:28,382 --> 00:12:29,115
Yes, Father.

129
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:31,520
Let's go.

130
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:38,870
Someone.

131
00:12:40,004 --> 00:12:40,830
Yes, Young Master.

132
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:43,360
Count the injured
and help the people settle down.

133
00:12:43,426 --> 00:12:44,315
Yes, Young Master.

