457
00:30:33,150 --> 00:30:35,320
(My heart feels like
it's about to explode.)

458
00:30:35,730 --> 00:30:38,999
(Master-disciple relationship
sounds forbidden and thrilling.)

459
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,080
