460
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:43,150
(Hey, Rong Shukuang.)

461
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:44,630
(Get a hold of yourself)

462
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,760
(and stop being obsessive.)

463
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:52,693
