let stray thoughts cloud their mind.

464
00:30:52,693 --> 00:30:54,048
What were you thinking about?

465
00:30:54,630 --> 00:30:55,520
You.

466
00:30:59,520 --> 00:30:59,910
No,

467
00:31:00,670 --> 00:31:01,760
